quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Shikhwa khubambula eshilifu shishio
  94,2,Ne nikhukhuruula omusiko kukwo
  94,3,kwali nikufunaka umukongo kukwo
  94,4,Ne nikhura hekulu okhurumbulwa khukhwo
  94,5,Ne bwatoto halala nende ubusiro khuli nende obwangu
  94,6,Toto halala nende obusiro khuli nende obwangu
  94,7,"Ne nonyoola obwiyangu, khola eshinani"
  94,8,Ne khu Nyasaye wuwo omulesi niye wokhalabanile
  95,1,Nditsuba khu tini nende zaituni
  95,2,Nende Khulukulu lwa Sinai
  95,3,Nende khulitokho lino liomulembe
  95,4,khubwatoto khwaloonga Omundu okhuloonga okhulayi muno
  95,5,Mana nikhumukalusia hasi wabali hasi
  95,6,"Halali balia Abasuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, abo balinyoola omurungo kulawa tawe"
  95,7,"Mana\tnishina\tnikhwakhamala shilakhuyingasia inyanga yo murungo"
  95,8,Kho Nyasaye Shali Omubusia Umalayo okhushila Ababusia boosi
  96,1,Soma mulira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi owaloonga
  96,2,Yaloonga Omundu okhurulana nende lilika
  96,3,Soma! Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi ni Omuhani Okhushila boosi
  96,4,Ulia wechesia nende ikalamu
  96,5,yechesia Omundu kalia akalali namanyile tawe
  96,6,Shikali kario tawe! Toto Omundu abetsanga omufuru
  96,7,Niyelola mbu ayindialile
  96,8,Toto khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niho amakalushilo
  96,9,Ulutsikhwo ulia ukaninjia
  96,10,Omusumba nalaama
  96,11,"omulutsikhwo\tye\tnaba\tnali khubulunjifu"
  96,12,Nohomba nalomesia okhuria Nyasaye
  96,13,Omulutsi ye nayingananga ne nakalukha inyuma
  96,14,Akorerwekhwo mbu Nyasaye alolanga
  96,15,"Tawe\tNalalekha\ttawe, khulamukhwesulula khuliboyo lieliswi"
  96,16,liboyo liobubeyi lietsimbi
  96,17,Ne mana alange abashie
  96,18,nafu khulalanga zabania! (abasikari bomulilo)
  96,19,Tawe! Olamuwulila tawe!Ne omwinamile (nosujudilaNyasaye) nomwisitiakhwo
  97,1,Toto efwe khwayishia (ikurani) mushilo shioluyali
  97,2,Ne nishiina shilakhumanyia mbu nishina eshilo shioluyali
  97,3,Eshilo shioluyali ni shiobukhala muno okhushila emiesi iyelefu
  97,4,Abamalaika bekhanga nende Roho mushilo esho khumunwa kwa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi buli mwikhuwa
  97,5,Omulembe eshilo esho okhuula mumabwibwi
  98,1,Shibali Abakhayi mubandu beshitabu nende Abatsokaasi bokhulekha akabali ninako okhuula kaboolele amenoosio
  98,2,Omurumwaokhurulakhu Nyasayeubasomelanga tsimbapulo tsioluyali
  98,3,Mukari mwatsio khulimwo nende amahandiko kakololokha
  98,4,Ne shibakabukhana balia bahebwa eshitabu halali nibakhamala okhuulilwa nende amenoosio
  98,5,"Nabo shibalomesibwa shiosi shiosi tawe halali okhulaama Nyasaye khulwa okhumutswenulila idini, Abandu abalunjifu, ne balumilile ukhulaama iswala, ne barusie izaka- eshihanwa. Ne eyo niyo idini yamemelo"
  98,6,"Toto balia bakhaya mu bandu beshitabu nende mubatsokaasi balinjila mumulilo kwa jahannamu, bamenyemwo tsinyanga tsiosi, ebo nibo ebiloonje ebibii muno"
  98,7,"Toto balia abasuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, ebo nibo ebilonje ebilayi mubandu"
  98,8,"Omurungo kwabu ewa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi ni emikunda chilaliwa, chiburangamwo emialo hakari wachio. Ako nikhu ulia oritsanga Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi"
  99,1,Olwa liloba liliseswa okhuseswa khwalio
  99,2,Ne olwa liloba liliyinia emisiko chialio
  99,3,"Ne Omundu aliboola mbu: ‘‘libeele lirie?”"
  99,4,Inyanga eyo liliboola amakhuwa kalio
  99,5,Khulwa okhuba Nyasaye wuwo alifimbulile
  99,6,"Inyanga\teyo\tAbandu\tbalirula mukhukabukhana bechesibwe ebikhole biabu"
  99,7,Kho ulia ukhola amalayi shinga obusiro bwoluloolo yakhakalole
  99,8,Ne ulia ukhola amabii shinga obusiro bwoluloolo. yakhakalole
  100,1,Nditsuba khutsifarasi tsitsitsaanga tsimbilo nitsiyesaana
  100,2,Nitsirusia tsinzesele tsiomulilo khukhupa ebilekeyi biatsio hasi
  100,3,Nende etsitsunushilanga itsuli
  100,4,Ne eno nitsitumuula olufu
  100,5,Mana nitsitsomokha hakari womukanda
  100,6,Toto Omundu ni Omukhayi muno wetsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi
  100,7,Ne toto ye mwene ni omuloli khu ako
  100,8,Ne toto ye alineshinani shiokhuyanza omwandu